1、认证接口
https://sandbox.ele-cloud.com/api/authen/token
POST 
Content-Type : application/json
请求报文{"appKey":"Mlfs7n9kofqPMaNVJSFoDcwS","appSecret":"awSW7gts8AS4StGV84HCKVCf"}
响应报文：{"access_token":"092a76b1-5eed-4ad3-bd0d-7d2da723cd52","token_type":"bearer","expires_in":24983,"scope":"all"}

2、接口调用

请求地址：https://sandbox.ele-cloud.com/api/xxxxxx?access_token=xxx
POST
Content-Type : application/json

以票据识别接口为例：
请求地址：https://sandbox.ele-cloud.com/api/ocr-service/rest/RecoImg/v1/ocr?access_token=092a76b1-5eed-4ad3-bd0d-7d2da723cd52
请求报文：
{
 "zipCode": "0",
 "encryptCode": "0",
 "dataExchangeId": "2234567kjx0000000000000000000029",
 "entCode":"123",
 "content": ""
}

响应报文：
